subject: <http://data.parliament.uk/writtenparliamentaryquestion/commons/2022-23/120948>
object: To ask the Secretary of State for Health and Social Care, whether Unispace Global Ltd fulfilled its contractual obligations on all PPE contracts it was awarded prior to its novation to Sante Global LLP.

subject: <http://data.parliament.uk/writtenparliamentaryquestion/commons/2022-23/120948>
object: The Department contract with Unispace Global Ltd for gloves was not fulfilled prior to that contract being novated to Sante Global LLP. However, in July 2021, a settlement was reached and the contract has now performed.

subject: <http://data.parliament.uk/writtenparliamentaryquestion/commons/2022-23/120948>
object: Department of Health and Social Care

subject: <http://data.parliament.uk/writtenparliamentaryquestion/commons/2022-23/120948>
object: 120948 [of Session 2022-23] on Unispace Global: Contracts given on 31 January 2023
